data.description: The newly constructed ranch home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an open floor plan. A metal 2-car plus garage at the rear of the lot that has alley access. Very well-maintained and tastefully decorated. Sellers have pets and would appreciate a notice to take them for a walk. A must-see to appreciate this great home. LOMR-F-Determination Document on file.  FHA assumable loan available.Call Corrine N. Bierly for your showing request.
